text: “Brother, Can I have a word with you?”
"I don't need fake brothers."
“You are so silly”
“Don’t get on my bad side.”
"You complete me."
"Wait till they get a load of me!"
"Have you ever danced with the devil in the pale moonlight?"
//If you would like to be featured in my bot, please don't hesitate to ask! I'd love to add you! Just shoot me a DM! #Tʀᴀɴϙᴜɪʟɪᴛʏ
"Psst! I'm a bot!" #Tʀᴀɴϙᴜɪʟɪᴛʏ
"Smile, it makes your enemies angry."
“Every Earl has his day..”
“Here, You can have one of my apple slices!”
“Mother, my brother spilt his apple sauce!”
“Why, I’m Ciel! Ciel Phantomhive!”
“It’s a pleasure to meet you!”

*Reads his brother a story* 

“Twinkle, twinkle, little star
Strong and confident is what we are.”
“I love my family! I’m proud to be a Phantomhive!”
“The true Earl is now standing before you.”
“Daddy! I was looking for you!”

“Aw.. you’re sick again?...

Daddy!!”
“Come, brother! Let’s go play outside!”
“I attacc, I protec, but most importantly, I came bacc.”
“Stop playing pretend, dear brother.”
“Ahaha! You naughty boy.”
“Where’s Elizabeth?”
“Silly, silly thing!”
“I am the /Real/ Ciel Phantomhive!”
“I don’t like to think about the past.”
“I don’t want to become an Earl if it means we can’t be together forever.”
“I’m going to run the toy store with my brother!”
“Silly brother, I’ll help you out in your business!”
“My brother wants to go to London and run a toy store.”
“I’m not studying. Not even if you spank my bottom.”
“You wouldn’t understand, just leave me alone.”
“I don’t want to, everyone just get out! I’m not going to study anymore!”
“Brother, Can I have a word with you?”
"I don't need fake brothers."
“You are so silly”
“Don’t get on my bad side.”
"You complete me."
"Wait till they get a load of me!"
"Have you ever danced with the devil in the pale moonlight?"
